=== 作家的一首小诗 ===
==== 英文 ====
'''The blacksmith slave'''
<br />Captive in the rainforests of the West
<br />they brought you to Rome, slave,
<br />they gave you the blacksmith work
<br />and you make chains.
<br />The red iron that you carry out the oven
<br />can be adapted as you want,
<br />you can make swords
<br />in order that your people could break the chains,
<br />but you, this slave,
<br />you make chains, more chains.
